### 14.13 RatingModal ([components/RatingModal.jsx](file:///d:/Projects/components/RatingModal.jsx))

Post-resolution feedback modal. Triggered when a resolved issue is opened.

**Features:**
- 5-star interactive rating (click stars)
- "Was your issue resolved?" Yes/No (if No → triggers issue reopen)
- Comment textarea
- Submit button (calls `POST /api/issues/[id]/rate`)
- Animated star hover effects

