## Chapter 18: Design System

### 18.1 Visual Theme

CivicPulse uses a **premium dark theme** with a **gold accent**. The design philosophy is "government meets modern tech" — authoritative but accessible, dark but not harsh, gold for civic prestige.

### 18.2 Color Palette (Tailwind Custom Colors)

**Backgrounds:**
```
page:   #0A0A0A   — Main page background (near black)
navbar: #080808   — Navbar, footer, sidebar
card:   #1A1A1A   — Cards, panels, modals
input:  #222222   — Form inputs, search bars
border: #333333   — All borders and dividers
```

**Gold Accent System:**
```
gold:           #F5A623   — Primary: CTAs, active nav, headings
gold-hover:     #E09010   — Button hover state
gold-light:     rgba(245,166,35,0.10)  — Tinted card backgrounds
gold-border:    rgba(245,166,35,0.40)  — Gold-tinted borders
gold-muted:     rgba(245,166,35,0.60)  — Muted gold text
```

**Text Hierarchy:**
```
text-primary:   #FFFFFF   — Main headings, primary content
text-secondary: #AAAAAA   — Labels, metadata, secondary text
text-muted:     #666666   — Placeholders, disabled, footer text
```

**Status Colors:**
```
status-pending:   #6B7280  — gray-500
status-assigned:  #3B82F6  — blue-500
status-progress:  #F59E0B  — amber-500
status-resolved:  #22C55E  — green-500
status-rejected:  #EF4444  — red-500
status-escalated: #DC2626  — red-600
status-reopened:  #A855F7  — purple-500
```

**Priority Colors:**
```
priority-urgent: #EF4444   — red-500
priority-high:   #F97316   — orange-500
priority-medium: #EAB308   — yellow-500
priority-low:    #22C55E   — green-500
```

### 18.3 Typography

**Primary font:** Inter (loaded from system fonts, or via `@import`)
**Mono font:** SF Mono, Fira Code

The font stack prioritizes system fonts for performance:
```
Inter > Segoe UI > system-ui > -apple-system > sans-serif
```

### 18.4 Border Radius System

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `rounded-card` | 20px | Cards, panels, modals |
| `rounded-input` | 12px | Input fields, dropdowns |
| `rounded-pill` | 9999px | Buttons, badges, tags |

### 18.5 Animations

Three custom animations defined in [tailwind.config.mjs](file:///d:/Projects/tailwind.config.mjs):

**`animate-fade-in`:** Elements fade in and slide up 8px. Used for dashboard cards and content areas.
```css
from: { opacity: 0, transform: translateY(8px) }
to:   { opacity: 1, transform: translateY(0) }
duration: 0.4s ease-out
```

**`animate-slide-in`:** Elements slide in from left 12px. Used for sidebar items and notifications.
```css
from: { opacity: 0, transform: translateX(-12px) }
to:   { opacity: 1, transform: translateX(0) }
duration: 0.3s ease-out
```

**`animate-pulse-gold`:** Gold pulsing ring effect. Used on key CTAs and active status indicators.
```css
0%, 100%: box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(245,166,35,0.4)
50%:       box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px rgba(245,166,35,0)
duration: 2s infinite
```

### 18.6 Button System

**Primary (Gold) Button (`btn-gold`):**
- Background: `#F5A623` (gold)
- Text: `#000000` (black)
- Hover: `#E09010` (gold-hover)
- Border radius: pill
- Font weight: bold

**Secondary / Outline Button:**
- Background: transparent
- Border: `#333333` (border color)
- Text: `#FFFFFF` (white)
- Hover: `bg-white/5` (subtle white tint)

**Danger Button:**
- Background: `rgba(239,68,68,0.1)` (red glow)
- Text: `#EF4444`
- Border: `rgba(239,68,68,0.3)`

### 18.7 Card Pattern

All cards follow this pattern:
```css
background: #1A1A1A  (card color)
border: 1px solid #333333
border-radius: 20px  (card radius)
padding: 24-32px
```

On hover: `border-gold/30` and `shadow-gold/5` transitions create a subtle gold glow. Transition duration: 300ms.

